seo: 主域名提取,URL处理,字符串操作
seo_en: main domain extraction, URL processing, string operation
summary: 该插件的核心意图是从URL中提取主域名并去重，主要用于处理和解析域名相关的信息。
summary_en: The core intention of this plugin is to extract the main domain from URLs and remove duplicates, mainly used for processing and parsing domain-related information.
